description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 77, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 77, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and 8 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50771-24982-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [77 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
